FT  10 APR 93 / World Stock Markets: Peru
FOLLOWING the March 3 debut of First Peru Investment Company, a Dollars 25m
closed-end fund from the Bankers Trust stable, Latin American Securities in
London is launching the Peruvian Investment Company, an open-ended
Luxembourg SICAV. The fund manager, Mr Federico Laffan, says that
'tremendous' opportunities now exist for investors in the Peruvian stock
market, as the country's radical reform programme takes effect.
